    <div class="gk-tip">
      <strong>Key count:</strong> India has <strong>28 States</strong> and <strong>8 Union Territories</strong> (as of 2020). J&amp;K was reorganised into 2 UTs on 31 October 2019 — J&amp;K (with legislature) and Ladakh (without legislature).
